==English==
===Etymology===

From Latin ''[[tricentennialis]]'', from tri + ''[[cent]]'' hundred + ''[[ennius]]'' year

===Noun===
'''tricentennial'''
# The 300th [[anniversary]] of an event or happening.

===Adjective===
'''tricentennial'''
# Occuring every three-hundred (300) years.

